reviewText: My 9 month old loves  Mickey Mouse Clubhouse.  His eyes light up when he hears Mickeys voice.  I plan on getting several more episodes as I cannot get then on Netflix or Hulu.  It is worth the money to see how excited my son gets over these shows!
